	   <tr><td colspan=2>I agree with all this effect is a joke,but asside from that the stats would look really great in my 28 mage. especially when i do max out my int..<br>On the mage inportance subject.  I more ot less wanted to represent the mages of sol ro and say all of your twinked out melee classes are missing out on a key figure of any group...Its not that i suck of have no skill but i have sat for up to 30 min looking for a group in the likes of FM,loio, and oasis, at 24 i could dd on average 161 per spell where as most non twinked melee's could hit for maby 25-30 and landing maby 2 every 4 times..lets see in that span of time lets just say 3 attempts and u did hit every time and i used my bolt of flame spell thats 90 damage caused by you (if u connect all three times-what your gonna loose for hp..putting strain on healers mana) and i cast 3 spells lets say 1 gets resisted cus it can happen thsts still and the recast dd is less at about 75.....humm 161+75 thats 236 no damage to me cus my pet is tanking and the only mana used is my own...and the clerics have plenty to save your butts from dying...so all you melee classes on sol ro when u see a mage lfg hook him him up it will be the smartest move u ever made...dont be jellous cus our epic is the balls and once we do get it we cant be beat.<br><br>truly yours<br>Kilkandark spiritguided<br>28 mage solro<br>DISCIPLE<br><br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
