	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Good<span id=notbold>[3.66]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>Effect: Everfount <br>Type: Triggered <br>Charges: Unlimited <br><br>Right-clickable effects are considered "Triggered"<br>Whereas procs would be listed as "Random" effects.<br><br>Also, class specific items usually cannot be used by other classes (effect-wise). Only those items which can be right-clicked from the general inventory slot can be used by any class. I'm pretty sure this earring has to be worn for the effect, which would make it mage only.<br><br>Hope that clears it up :)<br>&nbsp;<br>Odibil Lauxes<br>Magician<br>The Seventh Hammer</td></tr>
